 Alloy cadvisor exporter
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Alloy provides the &lt;code>prometheus.exporter.cadvisor&lt;/code> components that can be used to start a new cadvisor on the nodes. This is not required if the kubelet running on your nodes already runs cadvisor. This is the case for me on EKS running on Bottlerocket.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>